01:39:21,115 --> 01:39:23,276
l would go to the ice show.

748
01:40:53,807 --> 01:40:56,071
l'll trade you a favor
for a cigarette.

749
01:40:57,578 --> 01:40:59,842
The favor is,
steer clear of those guys.

750
01:40:59,913 --> 01:41:01,073
The Russians?

751
01:41:07,521 --> 01:41:09,751
They sure throw money
around here.

752
01:41:26,039 --> 01:41:30,738
The Russian is seeing this Natacha
Kirilova, the star of the ice show.

753
01:41:30,811 --> 01:41:33,974
He spends every evening
in the audience.

754
01:41:35,282 --> 01:41:39,048
- How'd you find that out?
- We went to high school together.

755
01:42:15,058 --> 01:42:17,583
Mikhi, is everything
all right?

756
01:42:17,660 --> 01:42:19,389
Everything is fine.

757
01:42:20,229 --> 01:42:21,662
Sweet girl.

758
01:42:23,733 --> 01:42:25,724
Go. Go on.

759
01:42:44,020 --> 01:42:45,783
Ladies and gentlemen...

760
01:42:45,855 --> 01:42:49,188
we are very proud to present...

761
01:42:49,258 --> 01:42:52,750
two-time Olympic champion...

762
01:42:52,829 --> 01:42:55,855
and three-time world champion...

763
01:42:55,932 --> 01:42:58,867
Natacha Kirilova!

764
01:45:06,496 --> 01:45:08,054
Let's go.

765
01:45:21,677 --> 01:45:23,372
Wait out here.

766
01:45:28,551 --> 01:45:30,143
Yes, he is.

767
01:45:31,754 --> 01:45:33,016
Hello, Mikhi.

768
01:45:33,089 --> 01:45:35,523
The meeting is not
until later tonight.

769
01:45:35,591 --> 01:45:37,115
The meeting's now.

770
01:45:40,429 --> 01:45:41,987
You have the money?

771
01:45:43,432 --> 01:45:46,993
Well, you know, we were going back
to get it before the meet.

772
01:45:47,069 --> 01:45:48,468
l don't think so.

773
01:45:50,406 --> 01:45:51,930
You have the money?

774
01:45:56,312 --> 01:45:59,281
l might have the money.
Where is the case?

775
01:46:00,349 --> 01:46:04,012
No, you have to do it.
l couldn't live with myself.

776
01:46:16,899 --> 01:46:18,526
l have the money.

777
01:46:18,601 --> 01:46:21,229
We conclude this now
and part friends.

778
01:46:25,775 --> 01:46:27,037
Where is the case?

779
01:46:39,722 --> 01:46:41,383
l'd like to be paid now.

780
01:46:47,063 --> 01:46:49,190
No doubt.

781
01:46:54,070 --> 01:46:55,833
Now tell me the other part.

782
01:46:57,273 --> 01:46:59,207
The other part?

783
01:46:59,275 --> 01:47:01,243
l'm leaving.

784
01:47:01,310 --> 01:47:03,676
l'm taking my fee
and l'm leaving.

785
01:47:05,915 --> 01:47:09,214
l have a person with a rifle
in the stadium.

786
01:47:09,285 --> 01:47:12,118
l've worked with her for years.
She never misses.

787
01:47:13,155 --> 01:47:15,089
l will call.

788
01:47:15,157 --> 01:47:17,682
l have to call within
45 seconds...

789
01:47:17,760 --> 01:47:19,751
to say that l'm leaving.

790
01:47:19,829 --> 01:47:23,196
And then in another ten minutes
to say l'm safe.

791
01:47:24,934 --> 01:47:28,301
Should l be unable to call,
your friend will be shot.

792
01:47:39,048 --> 01:47:40,481
Thirty seconds.

793
01:47:41,717 --> 01:47:43,241
We have to see
somebody inside.

794
01:47:43,319 --> 01:47:44,946
You can't pass
without badges.

795
01:47:51,560 --> 01:47:53,585
Twenty seconds.

796
01:48:03,973 --> 01:48:05,235
Ten seconds.

797
01:48:34,470 --> 01:48:38,907
There were two of them.
They were looking for those guys.

798
01:48:38,975 --> 01:48:41,375
Just a minute, sir.

799
01:48:57,960 --> 01:49:01,691
l am a Chilean citizen,
as you can see from my passport.

800
01:49:43,797 --> 01:49:45,059
Maman!

801
01:50:08,855 --> 01:50:09,879
Stay with him.

802
01:50:42,723 --> 01:50:45,283
Get out of here.
Get out of here!

803
01:50:46,193 --> 01:50:48,252
Get out. Walk away. Walk away!

804
01:50:49,996 --> 01:50:51,156
Go.

805
01:50:52,132 --> 01:50:54,123
- l will if you will.
- Just go.

806
01:50:54,201 --> 01:50:56,692
Come with me.
Forget about the case.

807
01:51:01,074 --> 01:51:03,634
l didn't come for the case.
l came for your boss.

808
01:51:05,412 --> 01:51:08,040
l came for Seamus.
l came for him.

809
01:51:09,416 --> 01:51:10,940
Just get out of here.

810
01:51:11,017 --> 01:51:14,350
l never left. Don't you see?

811
01:51:16,857 --> 01:51:19,724
Get out of the way!
Get out of--

812
01:51:26,366 --> 01:51:27,697
Get out of the way!

813
01:51:27,768 --> 01:51:30,464
You can't pass this way.
lt's blocked.

814
01:51:56,163 --> 01:51:58,825
l can take you in
or leave you here.

815
01:52:00,233 --> 01:52:01,825
That's him with the case.

816
01:52:01,902 --> 01:52:04,598
- Sir, over here, please.
- Wait, wait.

817
01:52:12,245 --> 01:52:15,271
There are more back there!

818
01:52:52,519 --> 01:52:55,249
All right. Stay where you are!
Don't move.

819
01:52:55,322 --> 01:52:58,382
Shut your fuckin' mouth up!
Shut your mouth!

820
01:53:12,672 --> 01:53:14,333
You stupid shite.

821
01:53:14,407 --> 01:53:16,341
You're a dead man.

822
01:53:40,133 --> 01:53:42,761
This is the BBC World Service.

823
01:53:42,836 --> 01:53:45,168
lt was announced today
after almost 30 years...

824
01:53:45,238 --> 01:53:49,004
of bloody and seemingly intractable
civil conflict in Northern lreland...

825
01:53:49,075 --> 01:53:50,804
that a peace agreement
has been reached between...

826
01:53:50,877 --> 01:53:54,472
the predominantly Protestant government
of that British-ruled enclave...

827
01:53:54,547 --> 01:53:56,071
and the lrish resistance--

828
01:54:01,721 --> 01:54:05,487
...have told CNN that it was the
apprehension and slaying in France...

829
01:54:05,558 --> 01:54:09,756
of the lrish terrorist Seamus O'Rourke
by parties still unknown...

830
01:54:09,829 --> 01:54:12,957
that contributed a stability,
largely allowing...

831
01:54:13,033 --> 01:54:16,730
the negotiations to proceed
to their historic conclusion today.

832
01:54:16,803 --> 01:54:18,361
O'Rourke had been denounced...

833
01:54:18,438 --> 01:54:21,202
by the lRA,
the military wing of Sinn Fein...

834
01:54:21,274 --> 01:54:24,505
as a rogue breakaway operative.

835
01:54:26,646 --> 01:54:30,138
Then, good knowin' ya.

836
01:54:43,296 --> 01:54:45,161
- l'm sorry?
- You said something.

837
01:54:45,231 --> 01:54:48,723
l said she would not
be coming back here.

838
01:54:50,670 --> 01:54:52,103
Yeah.

839
01:54:53,440 --> 01:54:55,374
She would not
be coming back here, would she?

840
01:55:01,314 --> 01:55:03,714
l can't even put my hand
in my pocket to pay the bill.

841
01:55:04,751 --> 01:55:05,911
l'll get it.

842
01:55:09,422 --> 01:55:11,287
l'll get the next one.

843
01:55:17,097 --> 01:55:18,394
What was in the case?

844
01:55:19,733 --> 01:55:21,598
l don't remember.

845
01:55:22,302 --> 01:55:23,530
Lesson number two.

846
01:55:25,538 --> 01:55:27,472
Keep in touch.

847
01:55:46,826 --> 01:55:48,418
Let's go.

848
01:56:00,874 --> 01:56:03,809
No questions. No answers.

849
01:56:03,877 --> 01:56:06,137
That's the business we're in.

850
01:56:06,270 --> 01:56:08,636
You accept it and move on.

851
01:56:09,707 --> 01:56:13,040
Maybe that's lesson number three.

